🎨 Tech Company Roles with Multi-Theme Toggle
This is a responsive and animated web interface showcasing various tech company roles using interactive cards. Users can dynamically switch between multiple theme colors using a dropdown menu. The site is fully built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript — using external files for structure, styling, and behavior.

🚀 Features
🃏 Animated Role Cards (Bounce, Pulse, and Grow effects)

🎨 Theme Switcher (Light, Dark, Yellow, Gray)

💾 Theme Persistence via localStorage

🧩 Clean separation of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript

🖥️ Fully responsive design

