Change the theme using the dropdown menu below the cards.

🧠 How It Works
Each card has animation on hover (bounce + glowing border).

Clicking a card triggers a scale/fade animation.

The selected theme is saved to localStorage, so it persists on reload.

Themes are applied by switching class on the <body> element.

